msgid ""
"Warning! Elten failed to verify server encryption key. It is possible that you"
" are not connecting to Elten server but to one prepared by hackers. It is also"
" possible that Elten Server key has changed. Any details should be provided on"
" Elten Website Forum. If no information about key change was provided, it is v"
"ery likely that you are vulnerable to hacker attack. In this cause any data th"
"at you will provide, including password, can be stolen. Are you sure you want "
"to proceed with this connection? Select No to exit Elten."
