#: src/scenes/loading.rb:318
msgctxt "Loading"
msgid ""
"Attention!\n"
"Since the release of version 2.5.2.1, new restrictions have been introduced fo"
"r globally banned users.\n"
"By default, they are prevented from speaking in any groups and writing to othe"
"r people.\n"
"\n"
"To allow banned people to speak in a group, change this option from the group'"
"s settings, General tab.\n"
"Similarly, to allow these users to write private messages to you, you must all"
"ow this from within your account settings, Privacy tab.\n"
"\n"
"Also, all groups moderated by banned users have been removed from most public "
"lists.\n"
"\n"
"At the same time, three changes have since been made to the premium packages a"
"t the request of users:\n"
"First of all, premium features are now visible in menus.\n"
"It has also been made possible to buy premium packages for a period of one mon"
"th.\n"
"Other billing currencies have also been added."
msgstr ""

